,"text":"NUNCA bolo IV en anafilaxia (excepto PCR)","guid":"n1kY6ydQQC63UkNkXnyFMQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"Requiere monitorizacion continua","guid":"9ckhd2mSTpm7iKhCkSwP0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"125","text":"ERROR COMUN → retraso en administracion","guid":"K-xS0shiRHKvw4O_aN-yhA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Principal causa de muerte evitable","guid":"Wb46jmsSRR-Vo4uiBOliQA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"124","text":"POSICION DEL PACIENTE","guid":"paXXAReuR2uqvN5LXRF7Gw","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"Trendelenburg si hipotension","guid":"opx3DvhBQPCD5YyK3WUi5Q","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"Semisentado si disnea predominante","guid":"NG6N_UyiSZmETzkbDIEe3w","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"NUNCA poner de pie bruscamente → muerte subita","guid":"LMUH9MsUTeSZ_VLhqv1UxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"124","text":"SEGUNDA LINEA","guid":"UV-73aGsSRmhbFRiGv-Hvg","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Fluidos IV agresivos","guid":"D7GzKJKaQA-EuuxvcBCG6Q","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"SF 0.9% → 1-2 L rapido (20 mL/kg)","guid":"fWNzY_GCRdSWszj_zf_dnA","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"Puede requerir 5-10 L en shock","guid":"fHYY_3ZsRNm0xX_K8NSgow","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"En adulto mayor → precaucion con sobrecarga","guid":"D2jgl2yYQCmAaJFi6un71A","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"145","text":"Oxigeno alto flujo → mantener SpO2 >94%","guid":"vl1cr0OxQASK4-it1ESizw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"145","text":"Nebulizacion salbutamol → broncoespasmo","guid":"Ogd3yih7QgOdJYgPH8IR8Q","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"5 mg NBZ, repetir segun necesidad","guid":"OB9sUEgBTvuHi-ZDwYuDGg","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"Ipratropio 500 mcg si betabloqueado","guid":"8Xh6a-ZWTQOxZf5UODPPpg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"124","text":"TERCERA LINEA (ADYUVANTES)","guid":"HeaEcRFoQZ2wCOpM0A97Cg","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Antihistaminicos H1","guid":"aEIGHSM2SsabYtyietIDlA","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Difenhidramina 25-50 mg IV","guid":"5Uu0FYoWQMKaegBb8me6TA","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Clorfenamina 10 mg IV","guid":"WVHYJkJnQfOeaZmZQZRdnA","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"Solo para sintomas cutaneos","guid":"Nr0tcRXQS9qqVp-ZOoJusw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"155","text":"NO reemplazan adrenalina","guid":"bmyXxvWfSZSfGhLZIAuG5g","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"155","text":"PRECAUCION en adulto mayor → efectos anticolinergicos","guid":"rxvyKgBZTWqZYIvDOSsnWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"154","text":"Antihistaminicos H2","guid":"NI7HL877SgW89AS5CBxVSA","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"Ranitidina 50 mg IV (retirada en muchos paises)","guid":"00nuzp0cQRuHfbQshIMFdA","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"161","text":"Famotidina 20 mg IV alternativa","guid":"BbsaaBqmRgCVycetNczHtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"154","text":"Corticoides","guid":"V47j-IVSQc-wtTlivbQn4w","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Metilprednisolona 1-2 mg/kg IV","guid":"HsFT-qnmRouf6PEANtuQmQ","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"Hidrocortisona 200 mg IV","guid":"1p9iRYuvQ9OgZhv-h9MwGw","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"Inicio de accion 4-6 h → NO utiles en fase aguda","guid":"J8uv3lRPSN2gab_fV3oigA","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"164","text":"Rol discutido en prevencion de reaccion bifasica","guid":"dIDiJ3EfTjuVnA656W2tVA","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"164","text":"Evidencia debil (Pourmand 2018, PMID:29759531)","guid":"EgtKkHOKQEmH5513zQ0ybw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"124","text":"ANAFILAXIA REFRACTARIA","guid":"dXlMEvPhTj6d3f_LdU4DDQ","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"Definicion → no respuesta a ≥3 dosis IM de adrenalina","guid":"vdOevLFZSM-F9dG85pTK3A","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"Infusion continua de adrenalina","guid":"lOIlelTqSkKz3d5jkCUO7g","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"GLUCAGON → si betabloqueado","guid":"deAcMgE3S5mniJmyGV3FHw","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"1-5 mg IV en 5 min","guid":"goVv6JFcSDG68CcJpbw0Ew","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Infusion 5-15 mcg/min","guid":"16S-WjmrR8aNCnwGPl5PnA","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"Efecto inotropico/cronotropico independiente de beta-receptores","guid":"s7vUKVdgSti5P2IspdnJtA","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"170","text":"Vasopresina 0.01-0.04 U/min","guid":"ChyOXk16S2ycKxrPKj62xA","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"170","text":"Azul de metileno 1-2 mg/kg IV","guid":"uqfArbeyTx2e5AmJ39ly6g","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"Inhibidor de oxido nitrico sintetasa","guid":"LRf3cT3qTXe30y4u-w_Zew","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"Util en vasoplegia refractaria","guid":"10kUyao4RyagQSXxuC5hmQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"170","text":"Considerar via aerea avanzada precoz","guid":"BZlDI9BjRxWO69xuA4ZFfw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"0","text":"REACCION BIFASICA","guid":"a-Befd_RR4OA3PDQX_RTIw","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"Recurrencia de sintomas sin reexposicion","guid":"vnG-W-hSTjOeOawBpdjrug","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"Incidencia 1-20% (Rohacek 2014, PMID:24725226)","guid":"Q_b-r4HDQDSOPsL9Pvl4JQ","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"Tiempo → 1-72 h post evento inicial (clasico 8-12h)","guid":"Vk3EiEpJSu-CxUcwESat5w","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"182","text":"Factores de riesgo","guid":"Hd3qIPx9SwGMUpU5konC3Q","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"Reaccion inicial severa","guid":"1H6dH_J3T8uqjhoJk9dbFw","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"Necesidad de >1 dosis de adrenalina","guid":"P9RChNUbS_qNnnwseOt2Nw","chi